data.description: Home under construction- Move in September! The Calvert features a spacious and open layout with a luxurious first floor owner's suite. Nest thermostat & wi-fi enabled garage door opener included. 2-car front entry garage. Upgraded designer kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, pantry & peninsula seating. Off the kitchen is the open dining room, great room & included sunroom! Upstairs are 2 large bedrooms and a full bath. The spacious first floor bedroom features a tray ceiling, WIC, separate vanities & double headed shower with seat. Enjoy water views and no flood insurance required! Chesapeake's only low maintenance, 1st-floor master villas with water views, access to the Elizabeth River & private beach. All w/ a low monthly HOA. CLUBHOUSE, POOL, FITNESS CENTER, PLAYGROUND & DOG PARK NOW OPEN - MORE TO COME! VIRTUAL & IN-PERSON APPOINTMENTS AVAILABLE
